<item>
            <title>[LU-18972] Implement llapi_lmv_get_uuids</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18972</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Implement &lt;b&gt;llapi_lmv_get_uuids&lt;/b&gt; method which is declared in lustreapi.h but not implemented. The change would be to add method implementation in liblustreapi.c. The implementation would be same as &lt;b&gt;llapi_lov_get_uuids&lt;/b&gt; but with different tgt_type.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This would allow users of lustreapi to list MDT devices.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There is an old Jira ticket ( &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5253&quot; title=&quot;utils: Remove prototype for function llapi_lmv_get_uuids&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5253&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5253&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; ) that has this discussion about adding this implementation but seems like this was not done for some reason.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
